trans-unit.source: Represents a subscription to a timer event.
trans-unit.target: Representerer et abonnement på en tidtakerhendelse.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] TimerEventSubscription objects are added to the timer queue associated with a workflow instance in order to send a message to a specific <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue> at a specified time.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]TimerEventSubscription objekter legges til tidtakerkøen som er knyttet til en arbeidsflytforekomst for å sende en melding til en bestemt <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue>på et bestemt tidspunkt.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue>

trans-unit.source: When the time specified by <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.ExpiresAt%2A> is reached, the workflow runtime engine sends a message containing the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.SubscriptionId%2A> to the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue> specified by <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.QueueName%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Når tiden som er angitt av <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.ExpiresAt%2A>er nådd, arbeidsflyten runtime motoren sender en melding som inneholder den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.SubscriptionId%2A>til den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue>angitte av <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.QueueName%2A>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.QueueName%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.SubscriptionId%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.ExpiresAt%2A>

trans-unit.source: The timer queue associated with a workflow instance is contained in the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.TimerCollectionProperty>.
trans-unit.target: Tidtakerkøen som er knyttet til en arbeidsflytforekomst som ligger i <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.TimerCollectionProperty>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.TimerCollectionProperty>

trans-unit.source: You can examine <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.TimerCollectionProperty> and the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueueInfo> objects returned by <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowInstance.GetWorkflowQueueData%2A?displayProperty=fullName> to determine which activities are waiting on a specific TimerEventSubscription.
trans-unit.target: Du kan undersøke <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.TimerCollectionProperty>og <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueueInfo>objekter ble returnert av <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowInstance.GetWorkflowQueueData%2A?displayProperty=fullName>å finne ut hvilke aktiviteter venter på en bestemt TimerEventSubscription.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowInstance.GetWorkflowQueueData%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueueInfo> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.TimerCollectionProperty>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.DelayActivity> and the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.SqlWorkflowPersistenceService> both use timer event subscriptions to provide part of their functionality.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.DelayActivity>og <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.SqlWorkflowPersistenceService>tidtakeren hendelsesabonnementer bruker til å angi en del av deres funksjonalitet.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.SqlWorkflowPersistenceService> </xref:System.Workflow.Activities.DelayActivity>
